        <h1>Śrīla Prabhupāda said</h1>
        <div><p class="text-justify">The following are quotes from mainly Srila Prabhupada’s correspondence, divided into various categories. Since years I am collecting Srila Prabhupada’s statements in regards to various issues and herewith I created for myself so to say a “dictionary” of Srila Prabhupada quotes which, despite being freely available.</p>
<p class="text-justify">I am again and again surprised, not many devotees know. Srila Prabhupada commented in great detail on many issues, never allowing us to forget that finally there is no material solution for material problems, the final solution can be found on spiritual platform only.</p></div>
        <article class="article">
